<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-48-1292 </DOCNO><TEXT>This report consists of the extended abstracts of papers presented ata workshop in Lyngby, Copenhagen, October 8 - 9th, 1986. The first versionof the OERESUND-database was ready to be released just before the workshopand we therefore wished to give information about the experiment andthe data-set available as well as present some preliminary results fromthe experiment. The workshop was aimed at participants in the experiment,scientists using the experiment data in their research such as numericalmodellers of meso-scale flow-fields and dispersion, persons with a generalinterest in the meteorological processes in a coastal area, governmentaland private officials dealing with air pollution abatement and assessment.17 refs. (EG).</TEXT></DOC>